## **Detailed Comparison**

### **Transform (Matrix4)**
```dart
// Most powerful, does everything
Transform(
  transform: Matrix4.identity()
    ..setEntry(3, 2, 0.001)  // 3D perspective
    ..rotateX(0.3)           // 3D rotation
    ..rotateY(0.2)
    ..rotateZ(0.5)           // 2D rotation
    ..scale(1.5, 2.0, 1.0)   // Non-uniform scale
    ..translate(50.0, 0.0, 0.0)  // 3D translation
    ..skewX(0.1),            // Skew effect
  alignment: Alignment.center,
  child: widget,
)

